<footer class="footer">
	<div class="container footer-grid">
		<div class="footer-col">
			<h3><span class="logo-icon">S</span> Sematec</h3>
			<p>Votre expert en plomberie à Bruxelles. Interventions rapides, professionnelles et garanties. Nous sommes à votre service 7j/7.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-col">
			<h4>Liens Rapides</h4>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/">Accueil</a></li>
				<li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
				<li><a href="/locations">Zones d'intervention</a></li>
				<li><a href="/about">À propos</a></li>
				<li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-col">
			<h4>Contact</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>📍 Av. Prince Baudouin 50, 1150 Woluwe-Saint-Pierre</li>
				<li>📞 0495750062</li>
				<li>✉️ contact@sematec.online</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="footer-bottom">
		<div class="container">
			<p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Sematec Plomberie. Tous droits réservés.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.footer {
		background: var(--bg-card);
		padding-top: 80px;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		margin-top: 80px;
	}

	.footer-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 60px;
		margin-bottom: 60px;
	}

	.footer-col h3 {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 10px;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.logo-icon {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark));
		color: var(--bg-dark);
		width: 30px;
		height: 30px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.footer-col h4 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		color: var(--text-main);
	}

	.footer-col p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.footer-col ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.footer-col ul li {
		margin-bottom: 12px;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.footer-col ul a {
		transition: color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.footer-col ul a:hover {
		color: var(--primary);
	}

	.footer-bottom {
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		padding: 20px 0;
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 40px;
		}
	}
</style>
